Background

Collaborative Site For Aquatic Preserve Water Quality and Seagrass Assessment All materials on this site are considered DRAFT work products. A map of the seagrass transect locations is provided below and a list of seagrass transects along with descriptive data used to summarize attributes of the transect for data management purposes is provided here: ### Transect List which can be downloaded for viewing and commenting.

Other tabs on this site include: Descriptive Statistics, Visualizations, and Analytical Results

Interactive Map

A Display of aquatic preserve seagrass transect locations and associated FDEP Waterbody Identifiers (WBIDs) is provided below. Hovering the cursor over the transect location provides the site name while hoverig over the polygon presents the FDEP Waterbody Identifier.
